p: HeLa cells were seeded onto 6-well plates at a density of 750,000 cells per well and incubated overnight. Cell monolayers were then infected with CHIKV-122508 at MOI 10 for 1.5h and washed 3 times with PBS. Infected cells were treated with proteasome inhibitors or vehicle control and harvested at indicated time-points up to 24 hpi.
